INDUSTRIAL SAFETY NOTICE:

This software generates code for industrial control systems. Users are 
responsible for:

1. Thoroughly reviewing and testing all generated code
2. Ensuring compliance with applicable safety standards (IEC 61508, IEC 61511)
3. Implementing appropriate safety interlocks and emergency procedures
4. Validating systems with qualified automation professionals
5. Following proper commissioning and testing procedures

The contributors make no warranties regarding the suitability of generated
code for safety-critical applications. Industrial control systems should
always be designed, implemented, and maintained by qualified professionals
following applicable standards and regulations.